# CRUD Implementation Summary

## Overview

Complete CRUD infrastructure for all entities in Trike Backoffice.

## CRUD Modules (/lib/crud/)

| Module | Entity | Operations |
|--------|--------|------------|
| tracks.ts | Tracks | Create, Read, Update, Delete, Publish, Duplicate |
| assignments.ts | Assignments | Create, Read, Update, Expire |
| progress.ts | User Progress | Create, Read, Update |
| forms.ts | Forms | Create, Read, Update, Delete, Submit |
| certifications.ts | Certifications | Create, Read, Update, Issue |
| users.ts | Users | Create, Read, Update, Invite |
| knowledge-base.ts | KB Articles | Create, Read, Update, Delete |
| notifications.ts | Notifications | Create, Read, Mark Read |
| activity.ts | Activity Logs | Create, Read |

## React Hooks (/lib/hooks/)

| Hook | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| useCurrentUser() | Get logged-in user |
| useTracks() | Fetch tracks with filters |
| useForms() | Fetch forms with filters |
| useAssignments() | Fetch assignments with filters |
| useUsers() | Fetch users with filters |
| useNotifications() | Real-time notifications |

## Business Rules Implemented

- Content defaults to `draft` status
- Autosave functionality
- Auto-playlist triggers
- Cascade progress updates
- Auto-certification issuance
- 9 auto-generated notification types
